title: Intro to Git
text:
Star

This little presentation was initially prepared as introduction to Git for master students in Statistics at Stockholm University


Aim
This presentation aims to give a very brief introduction to Git and Github.


Instructor

Mattias Villani Professor of Statistics Stockholm University


Before the presentation

Install git
Make a GitHub account
Consider downloading the editor VS code



Plan and material



More material
Books, courses and podcasts etc about Git

title: An Brief Introduction to Git
text:
Version control of you code and other files. Allow you to go back in time. No more:

Thesis.tex
ThesisMidTerm.tex
ThesisFinal.tex
ThesisFinal2.tex
ThesisReallyFinal.tex
ThesisReallyReallyFinal.tex

Collaboration. Work on the same code separately and merge later.
Development. Test new code features with branches. Abandon or merge.
Share code (GitHub)
